                </a>
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/people/Theeduassist/61576126813447/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors focus-ring rounded-sm block" aria-label="Facebook">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 8h-3v4h3v12h5v-12h3.642l.358-4h-4v-1.667c0-.955.192-1.333 1.115-1.333h2.885v-5h-3.808c-3.596 0-5.192 1.583-5.192 4.615v3.385z"/></svg>
                </a>
